<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225561>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Anoplodactylus evansi; A, southern Australian specimen; B, Tweed Heads, northern N. S. W. specimen. Pallenopsis macneilli; C, specimen from Eaglehawk Neck, Tasmania. Photo Andrew Newton; D, specimen from Tollgate Is. NSW. Photo Andrew Green. Meridionale chevron; male holotype, (SAM E 3681), E, anterior view. Meridionale sp.; male, (NMV J 57280), F, lateral view of typical form." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225561/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

